## Creating Issues

Use `gh issue create --repo {{repo}}` with the appropriate labels. Auth via `gh auth login` — no token files needed. Always explore the codebase for relevant file paths and line numbers before writing the issue body.

Alternatively, run `npx issueforge issue` in the terminal for an interactive wizard.
